def extract_hour(s):
    if (s != 'nan'):
        split = s.split(':')
        hour = split[0]
        amnm = split[1][2:4]
        result = int(hour)
        if amnm == 'PM':
            result = result + 12 
        else:
            result = -1
            
        return result 
    
df['hour'] = df.time.astype(str).apply(extract_hour)

df.date = pd.to_datetime(df.date)
df['month'] = df.date.apply(lambda x : x.month)
df['day'] = df.date.apply(lambda x : x.month)

In [42]:
#interactive map - colored by type, area ~ number of victims 
zoom_factor = 3 #initial map zoom 

my_map_1 = folium.Map(location = [40, -95], zoom_start = zoom_factor)

v_min = np.min(df_plot.color)
v_max = np.max(df_plot.color)

for i in range(0, df_plot.shape[0]):
    v = df_plot.iloc[i]['color']
    v_norm = (v - v_min)/(v_max - v_min)
    i_col = int(v_norm *256)
    current_color = matplotlib.colors.to_hex(matplotlib.cm.rainbow(i_col))
    folium.CircleMarker(
    location = [df_plot.iloc[i]['LATCOD'], df_plot.iloc[i]['LONCOD']],
    radius = 3*np.sqrt(df_plot.iloc[i]['victims']),
    popup = 'School: ' +  df_plot.iloc[i]['school'] +
    ' / City: ' + df_plot.iloc[i]['city'] +
    ' / Year: ' + str(df_plot.iloc[i]['year']) +
    ' / Type: ' + df_plot.iloc[i]['type'] + 
    ' / Victims ' + str(df_plot.iloc[i]['victims']),
    color = 'black',
    weight = 1, #stroke width in pixel
    opacity = 1, #stroke opacity
    fill = True,
    fill_color = current_color, 
    fill_opacity = 0.5).add_to(my_map_1)
    
my_map_1 #display
